      "title": "Create branch version workflow notes",
      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "# Create Branch Version In GenAsset\n\n1. Fill `token` from GenAsset Settings -> Tokens.\n2. Fill `asset_id` using **Copy asset id** from the target asset page.\n3. Fill `parent_version_id` using **Copy version id** from the chosen parent version.\n4. Queue workflow.\n\nExpected result:\n- New version is saved on the same asset.\n- `status_json` output includes `parent_version_id` and `ok: true`.\n\nNotes:\n- `asset_id` and `parent_version_id` are different values.\n- If you set both `asset_id` and `asset_name`, `asset_id` is used."
